### Welcome to GitHub Pages.

We believe in:
> _Science is the study of what Is, Engineering builds what Will Be._ 
> Theodore Von Kármán, 1957

We strive to: 
Research and understand the underlying principles of Software Engineering.
Engineer tools and techniques to aid how software systems are created and maintained.
